What you need to know:

Mbungo said he had good plans for Bandari to do well in the league, but was slowed down by the latest suspension of sports activities in the country announced by Presient Uhuru Kenyatta on March 26Although he has been urging his players to train individually, Mbungo said he can only gauge their fitness levels when they meet and train togetherMbungo is happy that his charges are slowly getting back to shape after the break as he works on restoring lost glory at the club